headline.print_headline: Ernst Wins Iowa Republican Primary for US Senate
headline.main: Ernst Wins Iowa Republican Primary for US Senate

lead_paragraph: State Sen. Joni Ernst has won the Republican primary for an Iowa U.S. Senate seat held for 30 years by retiring Democrat Tom Harkin.
